# 💻 Data Structures Used

| Feature                      | Data Structure                              |
| ---------------------------- | ------------------------------------------- |
| 🚦 Smart Queue               | `PriorityQueue<Appointment>`                |
| 💬 Doctor–Patient Discussion | `ArrayList<String>` or `ArrayList<Message>` |
| 📋 Medical History           | `ArrayList<MedicalRecord>`                  |
| 📝 Reports                   | `ArrayList<Report>`                         |
| 💊 Prescriptions             | `ArrayList<Prescription>`                   |
| 🥗 Diet Plans                | `ArrayList<DietPlan>`                       |
| ⏰ Reminders                  | `ArrayList<Reminder>`                       |
| 🔍 Doctor Finder             | `ArrayList<Doctor>` with filtering          |

